<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刹那间罗西变身成为火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是时候找出那个偷画的小偷了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西说着，冲向了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到达美罗城美术馆后，她大笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正在地上爬着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“侦探先生。”罗西笑着问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这么老了还在地上玩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱着眉头站起身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没在地上玩儿。”他说，“我在找这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探拿起一个棒球般大小的球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>球的一面有一个小的闪电图案，另一面写着“雾”的字样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”罗西说。“这是气象员的球！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对！”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他用这个气象球制造坏天气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我跟一位目击者聊过，她说盗窃案发生时美术馆布满了浓雾。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以没人看见是谁偷的画。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错！”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时他的电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂？”他说，“很好！别让他跑了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挂了电话后，看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“警察发现气象员正驾车行驶在西街上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在追赶他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一听这话，罗西马上飞出了美术馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>西街上，三辆警车正在追赶一辆黑色货车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>货车两边印有闪电的图案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然街道上布满了浓雾，警察看不到货车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>货车趁机转入一个小巷里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又是浓雾？”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这对于火箭女孩儿来说不是问题！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西深呼吸之后，用力吹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>浓雾立刻消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西现在可以看见隔着几条街的气象员的车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她朝着车飞去。嗞轰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用眼睛发射了激光，在货车后面烧了个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>货车马上停了，气象员跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你毁了我的气象货车！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会付出代价的，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>气象员从货车后面拿出一个气象球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把它抛向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气象球，激活！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个天空变黑了，乌云飘了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后——咔嚓！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天空中划过一道巨大的闪电。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它正向罗西逼近过来！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>